The President hasn’t done a single thing to help keep jobs in the United States. Instead, his tax cut actually raised incentives for companies to ship jobs overseas.
The President’s cut taxes for the wealthy and corporations on the backs of working people. He promised the benefits would trickle down. That was a lie.
